                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Company Name</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                        A unique business name ending in "Limited" or "LTD". It must not be identical or too similar to any existing business in the register and cannot contain restricted words. Use our free checker to verify yours instantly.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-50 text-brand-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 font-bold">2</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Registered Office Address</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                        An official physical address in the UK where formal legal notices and HMRC letters are sent. It cannot be a P.O. Box. If you value privacy, select one of our packages offering W1/EC1 London address options.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-50 text-brand-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 font-bold">3</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Director Details</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                        At least one individual director (aged 16 or over) who acts as the legal officer of the business. You will need their full name, date of birth, residential address, nationality, and corporate service address.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
