                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Shareholder Details</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                        At least one shareholder (can be the same person as the director) who owns the company. You will need their details and simple security answers (e.g. birth town, eye color) to act as an electronic signature.
                    </p>
