                    <button class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center py-2 focus:outline-none" onclick="this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('hidden'); this.querySelector('svg').classList.toggle('rotate-180')">
                        <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-base">What if my chosen name is already taken?</span>
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-2 hidden">
                        If your desired name is identical or too similar to an active business, the application will be rejected by Companies House. Our automated search tool pre-checks availability. If a conflict occurs, our support team will help you modify the name (e.g. by adding a modifier or changing "Group" to "Solutions") and re-submit it completely free of charge.
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- FAQ 4 -->
                <div class="border-b border-gray-100 pb-4">
                    <button class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center py-2 focus:outline-none" onclick="this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('hidden'); this.querySelector('svg').classList.toggle('rotate-180')">
                        <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-base">How many directors can a company have?</span>
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-2 hidden">
                        A UK Limited company must have at least one individual director (aged 16 or older) who is responsible for the legal governance of the company. There is no maximum limit to the number of directors you can appoint. Directors can be of any nationality and do not need to reside in the UK.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Final CTA Block -->
        <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-brand-navy text-white text-center rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-24 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600/15 mix-blend-overlay pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">Start Your Limited Company Registration Now</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">Establish a secure, compliant UK corporation in under 24 hours. Choose a plan and launch today.</p>
                <a href="/checkout?package=starter" class="px-10 py-5 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-2xl font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-brand-navy shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">Form My Company Now</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
